<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Connexion</title>

    <style>
        *, *::before, *::after {
            box-sizing: border-box;
            padding: 0;
            margin: 0;
            font-family: sans-serif;
        }

        body {
            min-height: 100vh;
            background-color: #fff;
        }

        .grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            height: 100vh;
        }

        .order__left {
            order: 1;
            padding: 40px;
        }

        .order__right {
            order: 2;
        }

        .centered {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
        }

        .no__overflow {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .form {
            max-width: 500px;
            width: 100%;
        }

        .logo {
            margin-bottom: 12px;
        }

        .header-logo {
            max-width: 180px;
            height: auto;
        }

        h4 {
            color: #867992;
            text-align: left;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            letter-spacing: 0.2px;
            line-height: 20px;
            font-weight: 500;
        }

        .alert {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 14px 16px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            margin-bottom: 18px;
            font-size: 14px;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }

        .alert-error {
            background: #fff1f2;
            border: 1px solid #fecdd3;
            color: #be123c;
        }

        .alert-success {
            background: #ecfdf3;
            border: 1px solid #bbf7d0;
            color: #166534;
        }

        .field-group {
            margin-bottom: 14px;
        }

        input[type="email"],
        input[type="password"] {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 12px 16px;
            margin: 0;
            display: block;
            border: 1px solid #c8c3cf;
            border-radius: 4px;
            background-color: #F6F5F7;
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #4F4659;
            outline: none;
            transition: box-shadow 0.25s ease-in-out, background-image 0.25s, border-color 0.25s ease-in-out;
        }

        input[type="email"]:focus,
        input[type="password"]:focus {
            border-color: #A26ED4;
            background: #FDFCFE;
            box-shadow: 0 0 0 0.25rem #ebd6ff;
        }

        .input-error {
            border-color: #e11d48 !important;
            background: #fffafa !important;
            box-shadow: 0 0 0 0.2rem rgba(225, 29, 72, 0.10) !important;
        }

        .field-error {
            margin-top: 8px;
            font-size: 13px;
            color: #be123c;
        }

        ::placeholder {
            color: #A29CA8;
        }

        .justify__space_between {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: space-between;
            margin: 30px 0 26px 0;
            gap: 15px;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }

        .remember-wrapper {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 6px;
        }

        input[type="checkbox"],
        label {
            cursor: pointer;
            outline-color: #B595D4;
        }

        .remember_me,
        .signup {
            color: #867992;
        }

        .forgot__password {
            color: #551A8B;
            text-align: left;
            outline-color: #B595D4;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        .forgot__password:active {
            color: #867992;
        }

        .login__button {
            outline-color: #734E96;
            width: 100%;
            border: none;
            background-color: #A26ED4;
            padding: 13px 17px;
            color: #fff;
            border-radius: 0.25rem;
            font-size: 16px;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: box-shadow 0.25s ease-in-out, background-color 0.3s;
        }

        .login__button:hover {
            box-shadow: 0 0 0 0.25rem #DAC5EE;
        }

        .login__button:active {
            background-color: #874DBF;
            box-shadow: 0 0 0 0.35rem #DAC5EE;
        }

        .signup {
            font-size: 14px;
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 32px;
        }

        .img {
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            object-fit: cover;
            display: block;
        }

        @media only screen and (max-width: 800px) {
            .grid {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
                height: auto;
                min-height: 100vh;
            }

            .order__left {
                order: 2;
                padding: 20px;
            }

            .order__right {
                order: 1;
                min-height: 300px;
            }

            .centered {
                align-items: flex-start;
            }

            .no__overflow {
                align-items: flex-start;
            }

            h4 {
                text-align: center;
            }

            .img {
                width: 100%;
                height: 300px;
            }
        }

        @media only screen and (max-height: 600px) {
            .img {
                width: 120%;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="grid">
        <div class="order__left centered">
            <div class="form">
                <div class="logo">
                    <img src="{{ asset('media/logo.png') }}" alt="Logo" class="header-logo">
                </div>

                <h4>
                    Bienvenue sur trouvemoi.eu, une plateforme haut de gamme conçue pour connecter efficacement particuliers et professionnels du bâtiment, avec exigence, qualité et performance.
                </h4>

                {# Messages flash #}
                {% for message in app.flashes('success') %}
                    <div class="alert alert-success">
                        {{ message }}
                    </div>
                {% endfor %}

                {% for message in app.flashes('error') %}
                    <div class="alert alert-error">
                        {{ message }}
                    </div>
                {% endfor %}

                {# Erreur de connexion Symfony #}
                {% if error %}
                    <div class="alert alert-error">
                        {{ error.messageKey|trans(error.messageData, 'security') }}
                    </div>
                {% endif %}

                <form action="{{ path('app_login') }}" method="post" novalidate>
                    <input type="hidden" name="_csrf_token" value="{{ csrf_token('authenticate') }}">

                    <div class="field-group">
                        <input
                            type="email"
                            value="{{ last_username }}"
                            name="email"
                            id="inputEmail"
                            class="{{ error ? 'input-error' : '' }}"
                            autocomplete="off"
                            placeholder="Votre adresse e-mail"
                            required
                            autofocus
                        >

                        {% if error %}
                            <div class="field-error">
                                Vérifiez votre adresse e-mail ou votre mot de passe.
                            </div>
                        {% endif %}
                    </div>

                    <div class="field-group">
                        <input
                            type="password"
                            name="password"
                            id="inputPassword"
                            class="{{ error ? 'input-error' : '' }}"
                            autocomplete="current-password"
                            placeholder="Votre mot de passe"
                            required
                        >

                        {% if error %}
                            <div class="field-error">
                                La connexion a échoué. Merci de réessayer.
                            </div>
                        {% endif %}
                    </div>

                    <div class="justify__space_between">
                        <div class="remember-wrapper">
                            <input type="checkbox" name="_remember_me" id="remember_me">
                            <label for="remember_me" class="remember_me">Se souvenir de moi</label>
                        </div>

                        <a href="" class="forgot__password">Mot de passe oublié ?</a>
                    </div>

                    <button type="submit" class="login__button">Connexion</button>

                    <div class="signup">
                        <label class="remember_me">Vous n’avez pas encore de compte ?</label>
                        <a href="{{ path('app_register') }}" class="forgot__password"><strong>Inscrivez-vous gratuitement.</strong></a>
                    </div>
                </form>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="order__right centered no__overflow">
            <img
                class="img"
                src="{{ asset('media/banner/register.png') }}"
                alt="Illustration"
            >
        </div>
    </div>

</body>
</html>